<p>The framework provides different loader styles, each animated with
CSS. They can be customized with size, color, scaling, and animation
speed utilities.</p>
<h3 id="doc-circular-spinner">Circular Spinner</h3>
<p><code>.loader</code> creates a <strong>circular spinner</strong> that
rotates a bordered ring.</p>
<ul>
<li>Use <code>.color-*</code> to set the primary stroke color.</li>
<li>Use <code>.border-color-*</code> to set the background stroke
color.</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="doc-examples">Examples</h4>
<div class="h-flex-start gap-3 mt-4">
<div class="w-48px h-48px h-grid">
<span class="loader place-self-center"></span>
</div>
<div class="w-48px h-48px h-grid">
<span class="loader color-orange place-self-center"></span>
</div>
<div class="w-48px h-48px h-grid">
<span class="loader color-red border-pink place-self-center"></span>
</div>
<div class="w-48px h-48px h-grid">
<span
class="loader color-green border-transparent place-self-center"></span>
</div>
<div class="w-48px h-48px h-grid">
<span
class="loader color-transparent border-cyan place-self-center"></span>
</div>
</div>
<pre class="html"><code>&lt;span class=&quot;loader&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;loader color-orange&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;loader color-red border-pink&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;loader color-green border-transparent&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;loader color-transparent border-cyan&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</code></pre>
