<h3 id="doc-pulsing-loader">Pulsing Loader</h3>
<p><code>.loader-grow</code> creates a <strong>pulsing loader</strong>
that expands and fades in/out.</p>
<ul>
<li>Use <code>.bg-*</code> to set the fill color.</li>
</ul>
