<h3 id="doc-sizing">Sizing</h3>
<p>There are several ways to size the loaders. The most flexible option
is to use the utility class <code>.scale-[ratio]</code>.</p>
<div class="h-flex-start gap-4 mt-4">
<div class="w-48px h-48px h-grid">
<span class="loader scale-50 place-self-center"></span>
</div>
<div class="w-48px h-48px h-grid">
<span class="loader-clip scale-75 place-self-center"></span>
</div>
<div class="w-48px h-48px h-grid">
<span class="loader-grow place-self-center"></span>
</div>
<div class="w-48px h-48px h-grid">
<span class="loader-dots-fade scale-110 place-self-center"></span>
</div>
<div class="w-48px h-48px h-grid">
<span class="loader-dots-spin scale-120 place-self-center"></span>
</div>
<div class="w-48px h-48px h-grid">
<span class="loader-comet scale-150 place-self-center"></span>
</div>
</div>
<pre class="html"><code>&lt;span class=&quot;loader scale-50&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;loader-clip scale-75&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;loader-grow&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;loader-dots-fade scale-110&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;loader-dots-spin scale-120&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;loader-comet scale-150&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</code></pre>
<p>For <code>.loader-dots-fade</code>, <code>.loader-dots-spin</code>
and <code>.loader-comet</code>, dots are generated with
<code>box-shadow</code>.</p>
<ul>
<li>The <strong>dot size</strong> depends on the element’s height.</li>
<li>The <strong>loader’s overall size</strong> is relative to the
element’s font size.</li>
</ul>
<p>You can adjust both independently to fine-tune the effect:</p>
<div class="h-flex-start gap-3 mt-4">
<div class="w-64px h-64px h-grid">
<span class="loader-dots-fade fs-xs place-self-center"></span>
</div>
<div class="w-64px h-64px h-grid">
<span class="loader-dots-spin h-16px place-self-center"></span>
</div>
<div class="w-64px h-64px h-grid">
<span class="loader-comet fs-5xl h-4px place-self-center"></span>
</div>
</div>
<pre class="html"><code>&lt;span class=&quot;loader-dots-fade fs-xs&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;loader-dots-spin h-16px&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;loader-comet fs-5xl h-4px&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</code></pre>
